            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Is this good enough...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wow, thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hello Pamela, Harol."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Why hello there Sophie, welcome."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sophie..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hello. Are you here to pray?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "No, I came to fix a clock."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It's a very old clock, but it's served very well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "The church had a clock?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Of course we had one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh, I didn't know... I've never seen it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Because it's not out in the open. It's in the back room."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "But you can hear it, can't you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hear it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh wait! Do you mean the bells?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's right. Good guess."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Those bells always ring at a set time, right? That's what we need a clock for."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll be leaving now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Thank you again. I'll see you next time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "See you later, Sophie."
        }
    ]
}